msgstr ":ref:`Ordersammanfattning <ecommerce/checkout/review_order>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:128
msgid ":ref:`Address <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Adress <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:129
msgid ":ref:`Extra Info (if enabled) <ecommerce/checkout/extra_step>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Extra info (om aktiverat) <ecommerce/checkout/extra_step>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:130
msgid ":ref:`Payment <ecommerce/checkout/payment>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Betalning <ecommerce/checkout/payment>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:131
msgid ":ref:`Order confirmation <ecommerce/checkout/order_confirmation>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Orderbekräftelse <ecommerce/checkout/order_confirmation>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:135
msgid ""
"Each step can be customized using the website editor by "
"adding :doc:`building blocks <../website/web_design/building_blocks>` or "
"opening the :guilabel:`Style` tab to enable various checkout options."
msgstr ""
"Varje steg kan anpassas med hjälp av hemsideredigeraren genom att lägga till "
":doc:`byggmoduler <../website/web_design/building_blocks>` eller öppna "
"fliken :guilabel:`Stil` för att aktivera olika utcheckningsoptioner."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:140
msgid "Content added through building blocks is **specific** to each step."
msgstr ""
"Innehåll som lagts till genom byggmoduler är **specifikt** för varje steg."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:143
msgid ""
"Restrict access to the :ref:`shop <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` "
"and :ref:`checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` for "
"specific customers, e.g., in a :doc:`B2B <../ecommerce/configuration/"
"b2b_b2c>` business setup."
msgstr ""
"Begränsa tillgång till :ref:`butiken <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-"
"access>` och :ref:`kassan <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` för "
"specifika kunder, t.ex. i en :doc:`B2B <../ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c>`-"
"affärsuppläggning."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:150
msgid "Order summary"
msgstr "Ordersammanfattning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:152
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Order summary` step allows customers to see the items they "
"added to their cart, adjust quantities, :guilabel:`Remove` products, "
"and :ref:`reorder products from a previous order <ecommerce/checkout/"
"reorder>`. Information on product prices and the taxes applied is also "
"displayed. Customers can then click the :guilabel:`Checkout` :icon:`fa-"
"chevron-right` button to continue to the :ref:`Address <ecommerce/checkout/"
"delivery>` step."
msgstr ""
"Steget :guilabel:`Orderöversikt` gör det möjligt för kunder att se de objekt "
"de lagt till i sin kundvagn, justera kvantiteter, :guilabel:`Ta bort` "
"produkter och :ref:`beställa produkter från en tidigare order <ecommerce/"
"checkout/reorder>`. Information om produktpriser och tillämpade skatter "
"visas också. Kunderna kan sedan klicka på knappen :guilabel:`Kassa` "
":icon:`fa-chevron-right` för att fortsätta till steget :ref:`Adress "
"<ecommerce/checkout/delivery>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:158
msgid ""
"Open the website editor to :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` checkout options such as:"
msgstr ""
"Öppna hemsideredigeraren för att :ref:`aktivera <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` utcheckningsalternativ som:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:161
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Suggested Accessories`: to showcase :ref:`accessory products "
"<ecommerce/products/cross_upselling>`;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Föreslagna tillbehör`: för att visa :ref:`tillbehörsprodukter "
"<ecommerce/products/cross_upselling>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:163
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Promo Code`: to allow customers to redeem :ref:`gift cards "
"<ewallet_gift/gift-cards>` and apply :doc:`discount codes <../../sales/sales/"
"products_prices/loyalty_discount>` or :ref:`promotional codes <ecommerce/"
"prices/promotional-code>`;"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kampanjkod`: för att låta kunder lösa in :ref:`presentkort "
"<ewallet_gift/gift-cards>` och tillämpa :doc:`rabattkoder <../../sales/sales/"
"products_prices/loyalty_discount>` eller :ref:`kampanjkoder <ecommerce/"
"prices/promotional-code>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:166
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Add to Wishlist`: :ref:`Enable wishlists <ecommerce/products/"
"additional_features/wishlists>` to allow signed-in users to remove a product "
"from their cart and add it to their wishlist using the :guilabel:`Save for "
"Later` option."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Lägg till i önskelista`: :ref:`Aktivera önskelistor <ecommerce/"
"products/additional_features/wishlists>` för att låta inloggade användare ta "
"bort en produkt från sin kundvagn och lägga till den i sin önskelista med "
"alternativet :guilabel:`Spara till senare`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:171
msgid ""
"If a :doc:`fiscal position <../../finance/accounting/taxes/"
"fiscal_positions>` is detected automatically, the product tax is determined "
"based on the customer's IP address."
msgstr ""
"Om en :doc:`skatteposition <../../finance/accounting/taxes/fiscal_positions>"
"` upptäcks automatiskt bestäms produktskatten baserat på kundens IP-adress."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:173
msgid ""
"If the installed :doc:`payment provider <../../finance/payment_providers>` "
"supports :ref:`express checkout <payment_providers/express_checkout>`, a "
"dedicated button is displayed, allowing customers to go straight from the "
"cart to the confirmation page without filling out the contact form."
msgstr ""
"Om den installerade :doc:`betalningsleverantören <../../finance/"
"payment_providers>` stöder :ref:`expressutcheckning <payment_providers/"
"express_checkout>`, visas en dedikerad knapp som gör det möjligt för kunder "
"att gå direkt från varukorgen till bekräftelsesidan utan att fylla i "
"kontaktformuläret."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:181
msgid "Address"
msgstr "Adress"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:183
msgid "Once they have reviewed their order:"
msgstr "När de har granskat sin beställning:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:185
msgid ""
"Unsigned-in customers are prompted to :guilabel:`Sign in` or enter "
"their :guilabel:`Name` and :guilabel:`Email` address, along with their "
"delivery address and phone details;"
msgstr ""
"Kunder som inte är inloggade uppmanas att :guilabel:`Logga in` eller ange "
"sitt :guilabel:`Namn` och sin :guilabel:`E-postadress`, tillsammans med sin "
"leveransadress och telefonuppgifter;"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:187
msgid ""
"Signed-in customers can select the appropriate :guilabel:`Delivery address`."
msgstr "Inloggade kunder kan välja lämplig :guilabel:`Leveransadress`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:189
msgid ""
"They can then :doc:`choose a delivery method <shipping>`, select or enter "
"their :guilabel:`Billing Address` (or toggle the :guilabel:`Same as delivery "
"address` switch if the billing and delivery addresses are identical), and "
"click :guilabel:`Confirm` to proceed to the next step."
msgstr ""
"De kan sedan :doc:`välja en leveransmetod <shipping>`, välja eller ange sin "
":guilabel:`Faktureringsadress` (eller aktivera växeln :guilabel:`Samma som "
"leveransadress` om fakturerings- och leveransadresserna är identiska) och "
"klicka på :guilabel:`Bekräfta` för att fortsätta till nästa steg."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:194
msgid ""
"For B2B customers, you can also :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` optional :ref:`B2B fields <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` "
"in the website editor."
msgstr ""
"För B2B-kunder kan du också :ref:`aktivera <ecommerce/checkout/"
"customize_steps>` valfria :ref:`B2B-fält <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/b2b-fields>` i "
"hemsideredigeraren."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:196
msgid ""
"You can add a checkbox for users without an account to sign up for a "
"newsletter. To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Settings`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Newsletter` feature, and select a :guilabel:`Newsletter List`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan lägga till en kryssruta för användare utan konto att registrera sig "
"för ett nyhetsbrev. Gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> "
"Inställningar`, scrolla ner till sektionen :guilabel:`Webbshop`, aktivera "
"funktionen :guilabel:`Nyhetsbrev` och välj en :guilabel:`Nyhetsbrevslista`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:200
msgid ""
"When the :ref:`Pick up in store <ecommerce/shipping/instore-pickup>` "
"delivery method is selected, the customer can :guilabel:`Choose a pick-up "
"point`, provided several pick-up points are available."
msgstr ""
"När leveransmetoden :ref:`Avhämtning i butik <ecommerce/shipping/instore-"
"pickup>` är vald kan kunden :guilabel:`Välja en avhämtningspunkt`, förutsatt "
"att flera avhämtningspunkter är tillgängliga."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:207
msgid "Automatic address validation"
msgstr "Automatisk adressvalidering"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:209
msgid ""
"Use the :doc:`Google Places API </applications/general/integrations/"
"address_autocomplete>` to ensure that partner delivery addresses are valid. "
"Addresses are automatically validated as the user types during checkout."
msgstr ""
"Använd :doc:`Google Places API </applications/general/integrations/"
"address_autocomplete>` för att säkerställa att partners leveransadresser är "
"giltiga. Adresser valideras automatiskt medan användaren skriver under "
"utcheckning."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:213
msgid ""
"To enable this feature, the :ref:`Google Places API <address_autocomplete/"
"places-api-configuration>` needs to be configured first. Then, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings`. In "
"the :guilabel:`General` section, enable :guilabel:`Google Address "
"Validation`, then paste the :ref:`Google Places API key "
"<address_autocomplete/generate_api_key>` in the :guilabel:`API Key` field."
msgstr ""
"För att aktivera denna funktion måste :ref:`Google Places API "
"<address_autocomplete/places-api-configuration>` konfigureras först. Gå "
"sedan till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> Inställningar`. I "
"sektionen :guilabel:`Allmän`, aktivera :guilabel:`Google-adressvalidering`, "
"klistra sedan in :ref:`Google Places API-nyckeln <address_autocomplete/"
"generate_api_key>` i fältet :guilabel:`API-nyckel`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:222
msgid "Extra info"
msgstr "Extra information"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:224
msgid ""
"You can add an :guilabel:`Extra Info` step in the checkout process to "
"collect additional customer information through an online form, which is "
"then included in the :ref:`sales order <ecommerce/handling/sales>`. To do "
"so, :ref:`enable <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` the :guilabel:`Extra "
"Step` option in the website editor. The form can be :ref:`customized "
"<website/building_blocks/form>` as needed."
msgstr ""
"Du kan lägga till ett :guilabel:`Extra info`-steg i kassan för att samla in "
"ytterligare kundinformation genom ett onlineformulär, som sedan inkluderas i "
":ref:`försäljningsordern <ecommerce/handling/sales>`. För att göra detta, "
":ref:`aktivera <ecommerce/checkout/customize_steps>` alternativet "
":guilabel:`Extra steg` i hemsideredigeraren. Formuläret kan :ref:`anpassas "
"<website/building_blocks/form>` efter behov."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:233
msgid "Payment"
msgstr "Betalning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:235
msgid ""
"At the :guilabel:`Payment` step, customers can choose a :guilabel:`Payment "
"method`, enter their payment details, and click :guilabel:`Pay now`."
msgstr ""
"Vid steget :guilabel:`Betalning` kan kunder välja en "
":guilabel:`Betalningsmetod`, ange sina betalningsuppgifter och klicka på "
":guilabel:`Betala nu`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:239
msgid ""
"When the :ref:`Cash on Delivery <payment_providers/inperson_payments/"
"cash_on_delivery>` payment option is enabled, the customer must click "
"the :guilabel:`Confirm` button and pay upon delivery."
msgstr ""
"När betalningsalternativet :ref:`Kontant vid leverans <payment_providers/"
"inperson_payments/cash_on_delivery>` är aktiverat måste kunden klicka på "
"knappen :guilabel:`Bekräfta` och betala vid leverans."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:243
msgid ""
"To make payment methods available to customers, configure and enable one or "
"more :doc:`payment provider(s) </applications/finance/payment_providers>`. "
"To do so, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Payment "
"Providers`, :guilabel:`Activate` the relevant payment provider, "
"and :ref:`configure <payment_providers/add_new>` it."
msgstr ""
"För att göra betalningsmetoder tillgängliga för kunder, konfigurera och "
"aktivera en eller flera :doc:`betalningsleverantörer </applications/finance/"
"payment_providers>`. Gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> "
"Betalningsleverantörer`, :guilabel:`Aktivera` relevant betalningsleverantör "
"och :ref:`konfigurera <payment_providers/add_new>` den."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:249
msgid ""
"The options displayed at checkout depend on the active payment providers, "
"the enabled :ref:`payment methods <payment_providers/payment_methods>`, "
"the :ref:`customer’s country and currency <payment_providers/"
"currencies_countries>`, and, optionally, the :ref:`maximum amount "
"<payment_providers/maximum_amount>` set for the provider."
msgstr ""
"Alternativen som visas vid utcheckning beror på de aktiva "
"betalningsleverantörerna, de aktiverade :ref:`betalningsmetoderna "
"<payment_providers/payment_methods>`, :ref:`kundens land och valuta "
"<payment_providers/currencies_countries>` och, valfritt, det :ref:`maximala "
"beloppet <payment_providers/maximum_amount>` som angetts för leverantören."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:254
msgid ""
"To display an :ref:`availability <payment_providers/availability>` report "
"for payment providers and payment methods and help diagnose potential "
"availability issues on the payment form, enable the :ref:`developer mode "
"<developer-mode>`, and click the :icon:`fa-bug` (:guilabel:`bug)` icon."
msgstr ""
"För att visa en :ref:`tillgänglighets <payment_providers/availability>"
"`rapport för betalningsleverantörer och betalningsmetoder och hjälpa till "
"att diagnostisera potentiella tillgänglighetsproblem på "
"betalningsformuläret, aktivera :ref:`systemutvecklarläget <developer-mode>` "
"och klicka på ikonen :icon:`fa-bug` (:guilabel:`bug)`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:259
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:41
msgid "Terms and conditions"
msgstr "Allmänna villkor"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:261
msgid ""
"To require customers to agree to the :doc:`terms and conditions <../../"
"finance/accounting/customer_invoices/terms_conditions>` before payment, open "
"the website editor and toggle the :guilabel:`Accept Terms` switch in "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab."
msgstr ""
"För att kräva att kunder godkänner :doc:`villkoren <../../finance/accounting/"
"customer_invoices/terms_conditions>` före betalning, öppna "
"hemsideredigeraren och aktivera växeln :guilabel:`Acceptera villkor` i "
"fliken :guilabel:`Stil`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:266
msgid "eWallets and gift cards"
msgstr "eWallets och presentkort"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:268
msgid ""
"Customers can pay with an eWallet or gift card during checkout. To offer "
"these options, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings` "
"and enable :menuselection:`Discounts, Loyalty & Gift Card` in "
"the :guilabel:`eCommerce` section. Then, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Gift cards & eWallet` and :doc:`create a gift card and/or "
"eWallet program </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/"
"ewallets_giftcards>`."
msgstr ""
"Kunder kan betala med en eWallet eller presentkort under utcheckning. För "
"att erbjuda dessa alternativ, gå till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> "
"Konfiguration --> Inställningar` och aktivera :menuselection:`Rabatter, "
"Lojalitet & Presentkort` i sektionen :guilabel:`Webbshop`. Gå sedan till "
":menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> Presentkort & eWallet` och "
":doc:`skapa ett presentkorts- och/eller eWallet-program </applications/sales/"
"sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:None
msgid "Gift card and eWallet options at checkout"
msgstr "Presentkorts- och eWallet-alternativ vid utcheckning"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:280
msgid "Order confirmation"
msgstr "Orderbekräftelse"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:282
msgid ""
"The final step of the checkout process is the order confirmation page, which "
"provides a summary of the customer's purchase details. A sales order is "
"automatically created in the backend. Enable the :ref:`Automatic Invoice "
"<ecommerce/handling/invoices>` setting to automatically send an invoice to "
"the customer."
msgstr ""
"Det sista steget i kassan är orderbekräftelsesidan, som ger en "
"sammanfattning av kundens köpdetaljer. En försäljningsorder skapas "
"automatiskt i systemet. Aktivera inställningen :ref:`Automatisk faktura "
"<ecommerce/handling/invoices>` för att automatiskt skicka en faktura till "
"kunden."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:288
msgid ":doc:`Order handling <order_handling>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Hantering av beställningar <order_handling>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:9
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce enables the configuration of products, categories, variants, "
"and pricing. It also manages customer accounts and access, supporting both "
"B2B and B2C business models."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Webbshop möjliggör konfiguration av produkter, kategorier, varianter "
"och priser. Den hanterar också kundkonton och tillgång, och stödjer både "
"B2B- och B2C-affärsmodeller."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:14
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:3
msgid "Products"
msgstr "Produkter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:14
msgid ""
"Configure products, manage their visibility, add images and videos, create "
"product combos, and attach digital files. Define selling strategies, "
"translate product information, and manage stock and packaging."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurera produkter, hantera deras synlighet, lägg till bilder och videor, "
"skapa produktkombon och bifoga digitala filer. Definiera "
"försäljningsstrategier, översätt produktinformation och hantera lager och "
"förpackningar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:22
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:3
msgid "Categories and variants"
msgstr "Kategorier och varianter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:22
msgid ""
"Use product variants and attributes to offer multiple product options. "
"Create attribute and e-commerce categories to better organize the shop and "
"product pages."
msgstr ""
"Använd produktvarianter och attribut för att erbjuda flera produktoptioner. "
"Skapa attribut- och webbshopskategorier för att bättre organisera butiken "
"och produktsidorna."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:29
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:13
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:3
msgid "Prices"
msgstr "Priser"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:29
msgid ""
"Configure different prices and taxes using prices per unit, pricelists, and "
"discounts. Prices can also be hidden, and sales can be restricted when "
"necessary."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurera olika priser och skatter med hjälp av priser per enhet, "
"prislistor och rabatter. Priser kan också döljas och försäljning kan "
"begränsas när det är nödvändigt."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:36
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:72
msgid "Customer accounts"
msgstr "Kundkonton"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:36
msgid ""
"Control access to the shop, the checkout, and the customer portal, and use "
"customer accounts to support B2B and B2C operations."
msgstr ""
"Kontrollera tillgång till butiken, kassan och kundportalen, och använd "
"kundkonton för att stödja B2B- och B2C-operationer."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:42
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:3
msgid "B2B and B2C"
msgstr "B2B och B2C"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration.rst:42
msgid ""
"Configure separate websites and shops for B2B and B2C businesses and "
"customize them to meet the specific needs of each business model."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurera separata hemsidor och butiker för B2B- och B2C-företag och "
"anpassa dem för att möta de specifika behoven för varje affärsmodell."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce is designed to fulfill the needs of both B2B and B2C "
"companies. It allows you to configure :doc:`prices <prices>`, "
"manage :doc:`access <customer_accounts>` for specific customers, "
"and :ref:`customize the website <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/multiple-websites>` to "
"support B2B, B2C, or both business models."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Webbshop är utformad för att uppfylla behoven hos både B2B- och B2C-"
"företag. Den låter dig konfigurera :doc:`priser <prices>`, hantera "
":doc:`tillgång <customer_accounts>` för specifika kunder och :ref:`anpassa "
"hemsidan <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/multiple-websites>` för att stödja B2B-, B2C- "
"eller båda affärsmodellerna."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:15
msgid ""
"While B2C businesses sell directly to the end consumer with a :ref:`tax-"
"included <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>` price, B2B businesses "
"usually :ref:`exclude taxes <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>` and "
"may even prefer to hide prices altogether, showcasing only their products "
"instead. To configure a B2B-specific online shop, make sure the :ref:`Tax-"
"Excluded <ecommerce/prices/taxes>` option is enabled, and complete the "
"configuration to :ref:`hide the pricing <ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>`."
msgstr ""
"Medan B2C-företag säljer direkt till slutkonsumenten med ett "
":ref:`skattinklusive <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>` pris, "
":ref:`exkluderar B2B-företag vanligtvis skatter <ecommerce-price-management-"
"tax-display>` och kan till och med föredra att dölja priser helt och hållet "
"och istället bara visa sina produkter. För att konfigurera en B2B-specifik "
"webbshop, se till att alternativet :ref:`Exklusive skatt <ecommerce/prices/"
"taxes>` är aktiverat och slutför konfigurationen för att :ref:`dölja "
"prissättningen <ecommerce/prices/hide-prices>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:24
msgid ""
"To make sure that only customers with an :ref:`account and granted access "
"<ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>` can see the prices, go "
"to :menuselection:`Website --> eCommerce --> Customers`, click the :icon:`fa-"
"caret-down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` icon from the search bar, and select "
"the :guilabel:`Archived` filter. Then click the :guilabel:`Public user` "
"card, go to the :guilabel:`Sales & Purchase` tab, and add the zero-priced "
"pricelist configured to :ref:`cover all countries <ecommerce/prices/country-"
"groups>`. Keep the :guilabel:`Public User` contact :guilabel:`Archived` at "
"all times. Website visitors now see the products without prices, while only "
"customers with an :ref:`account invitation <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"account-creation>` and an assigned :ref:`pricelist <ecommerce/prices/"
"pricelists>` can view the pricing in the customer portal."
msgstr ""
"För att säkerställa att endast kunder med ett :ref:`konto och beviljad "
"åtkomst <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>` kan se priserna, gå "
"till :menuselection:`Hemsida --> Webbshop --> Kunder`, klicka på ikonen "
":icon:`fa-caret-down` :guilabel:`Rullgardinsmeny` från sökfältet och välj "
"filtret :guilabel:`Arkiverad`. Klicka sedan på kortet :guilabel:`Offentlig "
"användare`, gå till fliken :guilabel:`Försäljning & Inköp` och lägg till "
"prislistan med nollpris som är konfigurerad för att :ref:`täcka alla länder "
"<ecommerce/prices/country-groups>`. Håll kontakten :guilabel:`Offentlig "
"användare` :guilabel:`Arkiverad` hela tiden. Besökare på hemsidan ser nu "
"produkterna utan priser, medan endast kunder med en :ref:`kontoinbjudan "
"<ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>` och en tilldelad "
":ref:`prislista <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` kan se priserna i "
"kundportalen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:36
msgid ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/B2B_B2C`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/finance/accounting/taxes/B2B_B2C`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:37
msgid ":ref:`Discounts <ecommerce/prices/discounts>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Rabatter <ecommerce/prices/discounts>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:42
msgid "Access request"
msgstr "Åtkomstförfrågan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:44
msgid ""
"When running a B2B business, you usually :ref:`hide the pricing <ecommerce/"
"b2b_b2c/prices>` on the web shop and make it available for :ref:`logged-in "
"users <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` only. To prevent anyone "
"from signing up freely, set the :ref:`Customer Account <ecommerce/"
"customer_accounts/account-creation>` setting option to :guilabel:`On "
"invitation`. To create a page where customers request access, open "
"the :doc:`website editor </applications/websites/website/"
"web_design>`, :ref:`create a form <website/building_blocks/form>`, customize "
"it, and in the :guilabel:`Action` field, select :guilabel:`Create a "
"customer`."
msgstr ""
"När du driver ett B2B-företag brukar du :ref:`dölja priserna <ecommerce/"
"b2b_b2c/prices>` i webbshoppen och göra dem tillgängliga endast för "
":ref:`inloggade användare <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`. För "
"att förhindra att vem som helst registrerar sig fritt, ställ in alternativet "
":ref:`Kundkonto <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>` till "
":guilabel:`På inbjudan`. För att skapa en sida där kunder begär tillgång, "
"öppna :doc:`hemsidesredigeraren </applications/websites/website/web_design>"
"`, :ref:`skapa ett formulär <website/building_blocks/form>`, anpassa det och "
"välj :guilabel:`Skapa en kund` i fältet :guilabel:`Åtgärd`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:53
msgid ""
"You can assign tags created on a contact form under :menuselection:`Website "
"--> Configuration --> Customers` to identify what kind of customers have "
"submitted the form. To do so, select a field in the form while "
"in :guilabel:`Edit` mode, click the :guilabel:`+ Field` button under "
"the :guilabel:`Style` tab, and set the field's :guilabel:`Type` "
"to :guilabel:`Tags`. Toggle the tags that should be automatically assigned "
"when a customer fills in the form and set the field's :guilabel:`Visibility` "
"to :guilabel:`Hidden`."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilldela taggar som skapats på ett kontaktformulär under "
":menuselection:`Hemsida --> Konfiguration --> Kunder` för att identifiera "
"vilken typ av kunder som har skickat in formuläret. För att göra detta, välj "
"ett fält i formuläret i läget :guilabel:`Redigera`, klicka på knappen "
":guilabel:`+ Fält` under fliken :guilabel:`Stil` och ställ in fältets "
":guilabel:`Typ` till :guilabel:`Taggar`. Växla de taggar som automatiskt ska "
"tilldelas när en kund fyller i formuläret och ställ in fältets "
":guilabel:`Synlighet` till :guilabel:`Dold`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:60
msgid ""
"When a customer submits the form, a new contact is automatically created in "
"the database. The contact is assigned the first pricelist from the list of "
"available pricelists, and, if applicable, the specified tags."
msgstr ""
"När en kund skickar in formuläret skapas automatiskt en ny kontakt i "
"databasen. Kontakten tilldelas den första prislistan från listan över "
"tillgängliga prislistor och, om det är tillämpligt, de angivna taggarna."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:64
msgid ""
"Submitted requests can be found under the :menuselection:`Website --> "
"eCommerce --> Customers`. Select the customer you want to :ref:`grant portal "
"access <ecommerce/customer_accounts/grant-access>` to. Once done, the "
"selected customer is able to view the B2B prices and products. Make sure the "
"correct pricelist is assigned to their contact form."
msgstr ""
"Inskickade förfrågningar finns under :menuselection:`Hemsida --> "
"Webbshop --> Kunder`. Välj kunden som du vill :ref:`bevilja portalåtkomst "
"<ecommerce/customer_accounts/grant-access>` till. När det är klart kan den "
"valda kunden se B2B-priserna och produkterna. Se till att rätt prislista är "
"tilldelad deras kontaktformulär."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:71
msgid ""
"It is also possible to hide the entire shop from the public using "
"the :ref:`Ecommerce Access <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>` "
"setting and only make it available for logged-in customers."
msgstr ""
"Det är också möjligt att dölja hela butiken från allmänheten med hjälp av "
"inställningen :ref:`Webbshopsåtkomst <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-"
"access>` och endast göra den tillgänglig för inloggade kunder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:74
msgid ""
"Configure the :ref:`checkout policy <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-"
"access>` to allow/disallow guest checkout for B2C businesses."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurera :ref:`checkoutpolicyn <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-"
"access>` för att tillåta/neka gästcheckout för B2C-företag."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:76
msgid ""
"Enable the :ref:`Shared Customer Accounts <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"multiple-websites>` feature to allow customers to use the same account "
"on :ref:`all <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/multiple-websites>` your websites."
msgstr ""
"Aktivera funktionen :ref:`Delade kundkonton <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"multiple-websites>` för att tillåta kunder att använda samma konto på "
":ref:`alla <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/multiple-websites>` dina hemsidor."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:81
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/prices.rst:334
msgid ":doc:`customer_accounts`"
msgstr ":doc:`customer_accounts`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:86
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:3
msgid "Multiple websites"
msgstr "Flera webbplatser"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:88
msgid ""
"Settings are website-specific, which means it is possible to configure "
"different behaviors for each website. For example, you can set up a B2C "
"website that allows :ref:`guest checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"checkout-access>` and displays :ref:`tax-included prices <ecommerce-price-"
"management-tax-display>`, and a B2B website that requires :ref:`sign-in "
"<ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` and shows :ref:`tax-excluded "
"prices <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>`. However, "
"each :ref:`pricelist <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` can only be assigned to "
"one website at a time. If you want to use the same pricelist on several "
"websites, duplicate the pricelist and assign each copy to its corresponding "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Inställningar är hemsidespecifika, vilket innebär att det är möjligt att "
"konfigurera olika beteenden för varje hemsida. Du kan till exempel skapa en "
"B2C-hemsida som tillåter :ref:`gästcheckout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/"
"checkout-access>` och visar :ref:`priser inklusive moms <ecommerce-price-"
"management-tax-display>`, och en B2B-hemsida som kräver :ref:`inloggning "
"<ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>` och visar :ref:`priser "
"exklusive moms <ecommerce-price-management-tax-display>`. Varje "
":ref:`prislista <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` kan dock endast tilldelas en "
"hemsida åt gången. Om du vill använda samma prislista på flera hemsidor, "
"skapa en kopia av prislistan och tilldela varje kopia till motsvarande "
"hemsida."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:99
msgid ""
"If you are running a B2B and B2C business, we *strongly* recommend to create "
"two :doc:`separate websites </applications/websites/website/configuration/"
"multi_website>` and assign a :ref:`zero-priced pricelist <ecommerce/b2b_b2c/"
"prices>` to the B2B website and a regular pricelist to the B2C website. In "
"case, you prefer using a single website, configure it using :ref:`country "
"groups <ecommerce/prices/country-groups>` and assigning :ref:`pricelists "
"<ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` to customers, and deactivate "
"the :ref:`Selectable <ecommerce/prices/selectable-pricelists>` option."
msgstr ""
"Om du driver både B2B- och B2C-verksamhet rekommenderar vi *starkt* att "
"skapa två :doc:`separata hemsidor </applications/websites/website/"
"configuration/multi_website>` och tilldela en :ref:`prislista med nollpris "
"<ecommerce/b2b_b2c/prices>` till B2B-hemsidan och en vanlig prislista till "
"B2C-hemsidan. Om du föredrar att använda en enda hemsida, konfigurera den "
"med hjälp av :ref:`landsgrupper <ecommerce/prices/country-groups>` och "
"tilldela :ref:`prislistor <ecommerce/prices/pricelists>` till kunder, och "
"avaktivera alternativet :ref:`Valbar <ecommerce/prices/selectable-pricelists>"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:111
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design.rst:30
#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/additional_features.rst:3
msgid "Additional features"
msgstr "Ytterligare funktioner"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:116
msgid "Invoice"
msgstr "Faktura"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:118
msgid ""
"Depending on the type of business (B2B or B2C), you might want to issue an "
"invoice. An invoice can either be generated automatically (for B2B) or on "
"demand of the customer (for B2C). This process can be automated if (and "
"when) the online payment is :ref:`confirmed <ecommerce/handling/sales>`. To "
"automate invoicing, enable the :ref:`Automatic Invoice <ecommerce/handling/"
"invoices>` setting. If this feature has not been enabled, the customer only "
"receives an order confirmation."
msgstr ""
"Beroende på typ av verksamhet (B2B eller B2C) kanske du vill utfärda en "
"faktura. En faktura kan antingen genereras automatiskt (för B2B) eller på "
"kundens begäran (för B2C). Denna process kan automatiseras om (och när) "
"betalningen online är :ref:`bekräftad <ecommerce/handling/sales>`. För att "
"automatisera fakturering, aktivera inställningen :ref:`Automatisk faktura "
"<ecommerce/handling/invoices>`. Om denna funktion inte har aktiverats får "
"kunden endast en orderbekräftelse."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:127
msgid "B2B fields at checkout"
msgstr "B2B-fält vid checkout"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/b2b_b2c.rst:129
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Order summary` page, open the :doc:`website editor </"
"applications/websites/website/web_design>`, go to the :guilabel:`Style` tab, "
"and toggle the :guilabel:`Show B2B Fields` switch to display B2B-specific "
"additional fields like :guilabel:`VAT` or :guilabel:`Company Name` during "
"the :ref:`delivery <ecommerce/checkout/delivery>` step."
msgstr ""
"På sidan :guilabel:`Beställningssammanfattning`, öppna "
":doc:`hemsidesredigeraren </applications/websites/website/web_design>`, gå "
"till fliken :guilabel:`Stil` och aktivera växlingsknappen :guilabel:`Visa "
"B2B-fält` för att visa B2B-specifika ytterligare fält som :guilabel:`Moms` "
"eller :guilabel:`Företagsnamn` under :ref:`leverans <ecommerce/checkout/"
"delivery>`steget."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo eCommerce provides multiple ways to configure, :doc:`present <../../"
"ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog>`, and sell different product options to "
"customers while organizing products by category for a better overview and "
"smoother navigation."
msgstr ""
"Odoo Webbshop erbjuder flera sätt att konfigurera, :doc:`presentera <../../"
"ecommerce/ecommerce_design/catalog>` och sälja olika produktalternativ till "
"kunder samtidigt som produkter organiseras efter kategori för en bättre "
"översikt och smidigare navigering."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:12
msgid "Product variants"
msgstr "Produktvarianter"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/categories_variants.rst:14
msgid ""
":doc:`Product variants </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/"
"variants>` are different versions of the same product, created by "
"combining :ref:`attributes <products/variants/attributes>` like color, size, "
"material, etc., which can lead to differences in price and/or availability."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Produktvarianter </applications/sales/sales/products_prices/products/"
"variants>` är olika versioner av samma produkt, skapade genom att kombinera "
":ref:`attribut <products/variants/attributes>` som färg, storlek, material "
"osv., vilket kan leda till skillnader i pris och/eller tillgänglighet."

